The Oblitercons/Serpentor/Nemesis Enforcer/Sixshot/Ares/Scattershot/Demon 
Wulf/Dark Claw/Flesh Ripper:




Dark One transformed to jet fighter mode, launching into the air, internal 
repairs activating.  He flew on the opposite side of Unitron.

---

Breakdown, Pyro, Hiss, and Scavenger marched quickly, following the shuttles 
and two jet fighters in the sky.

---

Unitron didn't react as Dark One arrived to help escort the shuttles, and 
merely continued on his way, matching speed with all the shuttles.

---

Nemesis Enforcer flew closte to Scattershot, snickering and talking about the 
Maximals, about how even if they were to win the Neo Beast Wars, all they had 
to do was remind them that Liono Prime had been their leader, and they'd 
retreat in shame.

Scattershot burst out in evil laughter, hardly able to keep up in the air.

---

Serpentor slithered along, internal repairs doing their job.

---

Demon Wulf and Flesh Ripper padded off after the other Alliance members, 
followed by Dark Claw in his war-vehicle mdoe.

---

Sixshot drove over next to Ares, and the two began to converse.

Sixshot:  Is it wise?  It's amazing Serpentor AND Unitron were able to escape 
the explosion that killed Koga Shuko and the others.

Ares:  They haven't tried anything yet.

Sixshot: Yet...
